                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_22201">Ruqaʿāt-i mutafariqah az munshiyān</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_22201">رقعات متفرقه از منشيان</title>
                     <note>
                        <p>Privately compiled collection or bayāz̤ for specimens of miscellaneous fine prose and poetry (including gīt and dohrah), in both Persian and Urdu (here termed Rīkhtah) or Hindavī, by an unnamed writer, possibly a munshīʾ by profession. </p>
                        <p>Not dated at end. 
</p>
                        <p>Nastaʿlīq, taʿlīq and ‘Indian’ taʿlīq on alternating tinted paper. 
</p>
                        <p>Folios occasionally disarranged. 
</p>
                     </note>
                  </msItem>
